data.description: ** Multiple Offers received, Calling for Highest & Best by 5PM on 02/29/2024**    Seller reduced the price for all the paint, flooring & other maintenance work. priced to sell. 3 Bedrooms and 2.5 Bathrooms home with a loft and basement - Premium private location with beautiful forest view to be enjoyed from backyard. House is sold AS-IS. High Vaulted Ceiling with Master Bedroom on the main floor is a great highlight ! New Roof in 2023, Newer siding, Leaf guard installed for peace of mind.     Additional Highlights !    * Woodland School District.   * Cul-de-sac premium lot (.39 acre).  * High Vaulted ceiling with windows offers lot of natural day light.
